display_long_description:
Welcome to Innerworld: a virtual world where you can learn evidence-based mental health tools and receive support in a place where you can feel safe being yourself. Start your mental health journey today.
 
CERTIFIED GUIDES
 
Work through life’s biggest challenges with guides certified in Cognitive Behavioral Immersion: a transformative approach to mental health support. 
 
SAFE, WELCOMING AND ANONYMOUS COMMUNITY
 
Join a tight-knit community exploring the thoughts, emotions and behaviors that shape us through courses, events and support groups.
 
LIFE-CHANGING MENTAL HEALTH TOOLS
 
Enter a virtual world that equips you with life-changing tools, so you can go back to the physical world more empowered than you left it. 
 
MEANING AND PURPOSE

Discover a sense of purpose by learning how to help others navigate life’s biggest challenges.
 
Let’s find our way together.

Innerworld is currently for people who are able to speak English.
